<style>
    :root {
      --ink: #2c3e50;
      --paper: #ffffff;
      --line: #d9dee3;
      --mute: #6b7c93;
      --accent: #0b6bcb;
      --bg: #f6f8fb;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 0 0 8px;
    }
    .subtitle {
        color: var(--mute);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .card {
        background: var(--paper);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }
    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
        margin: 16px 0 8px;
    }
    label {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    input[type="text"], input[type="date"], textarea, select {
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        background: #fff;
    }
    textarea { min-height: 84px; }
    table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 16px;
        background: #fff;
    }
    th, td {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 12px;
        vertical-align: top;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    thead th {
        background: #f1f4f8;
        font-weight: 700;
    }
    .notes {
        margin-top: 18px;
        background: #f0f6ff;
        border: 1px solid #c9defa;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 18px;

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            grid-template-columns: auto;
        }   
    }
    .sig {
        border: 1px dashed var(--line);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 12px;
        background: #fff;
    }
    .sig label { font-weight: 600; }
    .actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .btn {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: #fff;
        color: var(--ink);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .btn-primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    }
    .muted {
        color: var(--mute);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    @media print {
        body { background: #fff; margin: 0; }
        .btn, .actions { display: none !important; }
        .card, .notes, .sig { box-shadow: none; }
    }
</style>

<form id="marketScope" class="card">
    <section aria-labelledby="context">
        <p>
        This confirms that market scoping activities were conducted in accordance with Section 10 of Republic Act No. 12009
        and its Implementing Rules and Regulations (IRR), and considered in the Project Procurement Management Plan,
        consistent with the Principle of Proportionality.
        </p>

        <div class="grid">
        <div>
            <label for="projectTitle">Project title</label>
            <input id="projectTitle" name="projectTitle" type="text" placeholder="e.g., Procurement of ICT Equipment FY2026" />
        </div>
        <div>
            <label for="refNo">Reference / PR number</label>
            <input id="refNo" name="refNo" type="text" placeholder="e.g., PR-2026-00123" />
        </div>
        <div>
            <label for="endUser">End-user / implementing unit</label>
            <input id="endUser" name="endUser" type="text" placeholder="e.g., ICT Unit, RFO VII" />
        </div>
        <div>
            <label for="dateConducted">Date(s) conducted</label>
            <input id="dateConducted" name="dateConducted" type="text" placeholder="e.g., Jan 5–10, 2026" />
        </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="activities">
        <table aria-label="Market scoping activities">
        <thead>
            <tr>
            <th style="width: 110px;">Check (✓)</th>
            <th style="width: 38%;">Activity/ies conducted</th>
            <th>Documentation (as may be applicable)</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a1" name="activity_consultations" /></td>
            <td><label for="a1">Consultations with suppliers / contractors / consultants / professional associations or industry groups</label></td>
            <td>
                Highlights of consultations or meetings; proof of attendance; reports; summaries; screenshots; brochures; publications; price quotations; canvass sheets; Market Analysis Report or similar documents
            </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a2" name="activity_summits" /></td>
            <td><label for="a2">Participation in summits, fora, or conferences</label></td>
            <td>Highlights of consultations or meetings; proof of attendance; reports</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a3" name="activity_reports" /></td>
            <td><label for="a3">Review of technical, financial, or market/scientific reports</label></td>
            <td>Reports; summaries; screenshots; brochures; publications; Market Analysis Report or similar document; online product reviews</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a4" name="activity_brochures" /></td>
            <td><label for="a4">Review of product/service brochures, marketing materials, industry journals/publications, or related materials</label></td>
            <td>Reports; summaries; screenshots; brochures; publications; online product reviews</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a5" name="activity_price_sourcing" /></td>
            <td><label for="a5">Price sourcing for quotations or cost estimates from suppliers, contractors, or consultants</label></td>
            <td>Price quotations; canvass sheets; online product reviews</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a6" name="activity_philgeps" /></td>
            <td><label for="a6">Use of data from PhilGEPS or agency websites</label></td>
            <td>Reports; summaries; screenshots; price quotations; canvass sheets; PhilGEPS postings; online product reviews</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td><input type="checkbox" id="a7" name="activity_other" /></td>
            <td><label for="a7">Other analogous market scoping activity/ies undertaken</label></td>
            <td>
                <textarea name="other_docs" placeholder="Describe the activity and attach or list documentation (e.g., links, file names, references)"></textarea>
            </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>

    <section class="notes" aria-labelledby="notes">
        <strong>Notes:</strong>
        <ul>
        <li>The market scoping activities shall be identified and undertaken at the option of the End-User or Implementing Unit based on its needs and objectives.</li>
        <li>The list of supporting documents in the Documentation column is not exclusive and may include other documents that may be gathered by the End-User or Implementing Unit pertinent to the activity/ies conducted.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="footer-grid" aria-labelledby="signatures">
        <div class="sig">
        <label for="preparedBy">Prepared by</label>
        <input id="preparedBy" name="preparedBy" type="text" placeholder="Name, Position" />
        <div class="grid" style="margin-top:8px;">
            <div>
            <label for="preparedDate">Date</label>
            <input id="preparedDate" name="preparedDate" type="date" />
            </div>
            <div>
            <label for="preparedSignature">Signature/Initials</label>
            <input id="preparedSignature" name="preparedSignature" type="text" placeholder="Initials or signature reference" />
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig">
        <label for="reviewedBy">Reviewed/validated by</label>
        <input id="reviewedBy" name="reviewedBy" type="text" placeholder="Name, Position" />
        <div class="grid" style="margin-top:8px;">
            <div>
            <label for="reviewedDate">Date</label>
            <input id="reviewedDate" name="reviewedDate" type="date" />
            </div>
            <div>
            <label for="reviewedSignature">Signature/Initials</label>
            <input id="reviewedSignature" name="reviewedSignature" type="text" placeholder="Initials or signature reference" />
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="actions">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Confirm</button>
        <button type="reset" class="btn">Clear</button>
        <span class="muted">Save or print after completing fields and checking applicable activities.</span>
    </div>
</form>